---
// Section 18: Product Governance
---

<div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
  <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">Section 18: Product Governance</h2>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Decision Making</h3>
  <table class="mb-6 w-full border-collapse text-sm">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90">Area</th>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90"
          >Decision Maker</th
        >
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90"
          >Input From</th
        >
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Product vision</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Cady (Lead)</td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">All team</td></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Architecture</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Cady + Jorsh</td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Aura for infra</td></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Technical implementation</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Jorsh</td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Code review required</td></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Infrastructure</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Aura</td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Team approval for costs</td></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Security</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Consensus</td
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">All team</td></tr
      >
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Code Review Policy</h3>
  <div class="mb-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] p-4">
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70">
      <li>All changes require PR review</li>
      <li>At least one approval before merge</li>
      <li>CI must pass (build + tests)</li>
      <li>Security-sensitive changes require two approvals</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Communication</h3>
  <table class="mb-6 w-full border-collapse text-sm">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90"
          >Channel</th
        >
        <th class="border border-white/10 bg-white/5 px-2.5 py-2 text-left text-white/90"
          >Purpose</th
        >
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Discord</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Day-to-day communication</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">GitHub Issues</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Bug reports, feature requests</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Azure DevOps</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Sprint planning, work items</td
        ></tr
      >
      <tr
        ><td class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Weekly sync</td><td
          class="border border-white/10 px-2.5 py-2 align-top">Progress review, blockers</td
        ></tr
      >
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-400">Documentation Standards</h3>
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-500/35 bg-indigo-500/[0.12] p-4">
    Architecture decisions documented in ADRs (Architecture Decision Records). API contracts defined
    before implementation. CLAUDE.md keeps Claude Code informed.
  </div>
</div>
